                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 235.) I was sent for to the shop, and found the prisoner—I received this box from Dugard—I searched the prisoner at the station ten minutes afterwards, and found seven shillings five sixpences, aud two halfpence—when I was taking him to Worship-street he laughed and said, "I am glad my <hi rend="italic">pal</hi> got away."</p>
